snippet.title: Munchkin: Quacked Quest - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Munchkin: Quacked Quest is now available on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch and Steam! http://ow.ly/byuR50wVh8L

Welcome to the glorious world of Munchkin, where those daring enough among you will defy the best wishes of your party and friends to become THE ULTIMATE! If you are someone who would backstab your allies to claim that epic new item, then Munchkin: Quacked Quest is the game for you...

✨ Steal treasures!
☠️ Kill monsters!
🦆 Grab ducks!
🏆 Overcome your opponents! 

🎉 Enter the quackiest squad on Facebook: https://facebook.com/DigitalMunchkin/
👑 Claim your duck on Twitter: https://twitter.com/DigitalMunchkin

Asmodee Digital's social channels can be found below:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/AsmodeeDigital
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/AsmodeeDigital
Twitter: https://twitter.com/AsmodeeDigital
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/asmodeedigital
